  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示患者从社区到住院的完整路径，以及导致急诊滞留的瓶颈机制。核心是要解释access block是怎么形成的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "Inpatient",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。起点是Community社区，然后分流到GP和急诊到达两条路径对吗？GP也会转介到急诊？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Community同时连接GP和ED_Arrival，GP也会导向ED_Arrival。很多患者其实先看了GP还是被送到急诊。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Community、GP、ED_Arrival三个节点画好了。GP我用浅蓝色填充，和急诊区分开。接下来是ED assessment & treatment？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ED_Treat是核心状态节点，用红色系表示。然后到Decision to admit决定住院，再到Inpatient stay住院状态，最后Ready for discharge准备出院。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "主流程画完了：ED_Treat红色状态→Admission决策点→Inpatient红色状态→Ready准备出院。现在是要画那两个blockages瓶颈吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这是关键。从Ready分出两个约束：Aged care placement老年护理床位不足，和NDIS supports住宿支持延迟。这两个用橙色虚线框，表示风险节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Block_Aged和Block_NDIS都加上了，橙色虚线边框。但这两个只是挂在那里吗？还是需要表达它们如何造成access block？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要画feedback loop反馈循环。Block_Aged通过occupancy feedback loop虚线连回Inpatient，表示床位被占满。另外Inpatient还要连一条虚线到ED_Treat，表示高占用限制了急诊流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat",
        "occupancy feedback loop",
        "high occupancy limits flow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解了，就是恶性循环：出院受阻→床位占满→急诊患者进不来。这两条都用虚线表示反馈关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat",
        "feedback"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。Block_Aged到Inpatient标注occupancy feedback loop，Inpatient到ED_Treat标注high occupancy limits flow。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat",
        "occupancy feedback loop",
        "high occupancy limits flow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
